<h2 id="technologies-used">Technologies Used</h2>

<h3 id="back-end">Back-end</h3>

<ul>
  <li>For handling server requests: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Node.js with Express.js Framework</code></li>
  <li>WebHook: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Setuped with Facebook Messenger</code></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="front-end">Front-end</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Resume File Type: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">LaTeX</code></li>
  <li>Styling: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">CSS</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">BOOTSTRAP</code></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="others">Others</h3>

